file.name: requiredFormParamsTest.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Test Api
  version: '3.0.0'

paths:
  /test_required:
    post:
      summary: Operation with form body that is required
      operationId: get_with_required_body
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/x-www-form-urlencoded:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/Category'
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Success

  /test_optional:
    post:
      summary: Operation with form body that is optional
      operationId: get_with_optional_body
      requestBody:
        required: false
        content:
          application/x-www-form-urlencoded:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/Category'
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Success

components:
  schemas:
    Category:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        name:
          type: string
